{"tid":1094741,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU率先豪捐1億助江原道災民 江南大叔PSY接力響應","createTime":"2019-04-06T13:54:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T16:08:36.000Z","uid":34643,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"707a0f2da1e5f7e961fad04c4956eae04282cd13","tid":1094741,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T13:54:01.000Z","msg":"韓國「江原道大火」失控延燒，已經成為國家級災難，政府頒布「災難最高緊急狀態」，動員所有人力物力救火。國難當頭，演藝圈不少藝人拋磚引玉，率先捐出善款，IU一口氣就捐了一億韓幣，讓兒童福利機構可以去幫助災區的孩童們。PSY今天也捐出一億韓元，希望災民早日重建家園。<br />\n<br />\n由於大火延燒面積廣大，許多韓劇取景的地方皆付之一炬，災後重建之路迢迢。身為江原道鄉親，金希澈率先捐出3000萬韓幣，剛開完台灣見面會的南柱赫也慷慨解囊，同樣捐助3000萬韓幣。2PM的俊昊、宋仲基也是各捐3000萬元。老家也在江原道的尹智聖捐出1000萬韓幣，車銀優、金裕貞、丁一宇、金所炫等藝人也都以千萬為單位對災難救助協會捐出善款。<br />\n<br />\n除了老家在江原道的藝人們，像是宋仲基曾在江原道當兵，多名演員也都在江原道取景過，對當地有著不同的情感。粉絲也自發性以藝人名義代為捐款，協會陸續收到署名為姜丹尼爾、EXO、防彈少年團等粉絲小額捐款，聚沙成塔數字同樣相當可觀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.wenweipo.com/2019/04/06/a15a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.wenweipo.com%2F2019%2F04%2F06%2Fa15a.jpg&h=1ebd6223&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"481b017ee0de22fde78825bf95327032366adb91","tid":1094741,"uid":196924,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T14:03:25.000Z","msg":"老家也在江原道的尹智聖捐出1000萬韓幣<br />\n1000萬韓幣 = 港紙7萬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老家燒成咁先捐得幾皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e8f4b0fd2281def9cc64ba7997e8275098484f7","tid":1094741,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"481b017ee0de22fde78825bf95327032366adb91","tid":1094741,"uid":196924,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T14:03:25.000Z","msg":"老家也在江原道的尹智聖捐出1000萬韓幣<br />\n1000萬韓幣 = 港紙7萬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老家燒成咁先捐得幾皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T14:12:38.000Z","msg":"唔可以咁仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d99d06c63a42e0866ab86afac1a340c1367be10","tid":1094741,"uid":61748,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T14:15:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f845a08c6eb15689d0ff214599e9c206f9e0a7fb","tid":1094741,"uid":81273,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"0d99d06c63a42e0866ab86afac1a340c1367be10","tid":1094741,"uid":61748,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T14:15:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T14:19:34.000Z","msg":"毒撚好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3965daed48d67213df62722e11be84a8577aa15a","tid":1094741,"uid":7699,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T14:21:56.000Z","msg":"有時會諗我前世做左咩好事 今世會有IU呢個咁好嘅老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20950046b0aa95a5921baf756d2a3726153285fd","tid":1094741,"uid":179051,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T14:25:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d02293ce37e40b082c934f9b055864c1b1ac219f","tid":1094741,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T14:29:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"468813f06504ca873633aef232b264b7ad8abc5e","tid":1094741,"uid":34643,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3965daed48d67213df62722e11be84a8577aa15a","tid":1094741,"uid":7699,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,